sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Orch as Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>rustls TLS 1.2+
    participant TGIS as TGIS Server<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant NLP as Caikit NLP<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant OpenAI as OpenAI Server (vLLM)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Chunker as Chunker Service<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Detector as Detector Service(s)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant OTel as OTel Collector<br/>4317/TCP

    Note over Client,Detector: Flow 1: Unary Text Generation with Detection (v1)

    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v1/task/classification-with-text-generation<br/>Auth: Header passthrough (X-Forwarded-Access-Token)
    Orch->>TGIS: GenerationService.Generate (gRPC)<br/>Auth: mm-model-id header
    TGIS-->>Orch: GenerateResponse (generated text)
    Orch->>Chunker: ChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict (gRPC)<br/>Auth: mm-model-id header
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked tokens
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Auth: detector-id, x-model-name headers
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results (classifications)
    Orch-->>Client: JSON response with text + detections
    Orch--)OTel: OTLP traces/metrics (async)

    Note over Client,Detector: Flow 2: Streaming Chat Completions with Detection (v2)

    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Auth: Header passthrough
    Orch->>OpenAI: POST /v1/chat/completions (stream=true)<br/>Auth: Header passthrough
    loop SSE stream chunks
        OpenAI-->>Orch: SSE data chunks
        Orch->>Chunker: BidiStreamingChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict<br/>(bidirectional gRPC stream)
        Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked tokens
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>(batched detection)
        Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
        Orch-->>Client: SSE data (text + detections)
    end
    Orch--)OTel: OTLP traces/metrics (async)

    Note over Client,Detector: Flow 3: Standalone Content Detection (v2)

    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/detection/content<br/>Auth: Header passthrough
    Orch->>Chunker: ChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict (gRPC)<br/>Auth: mm-model-id header
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked tokens
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Auth: detector-id header
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: JSON detection response
    Orch--)OTel: OTLP traces/metrics (async)
